Description: Comprehensive five-stage workflow for differential expression (DE) analysis. Execution of DE analysis with default parameter with seven or six R packages: DeSeq2, EBSeq, edgeR, KnowSeq, limma, NOISeq, SAMSeq. Combine the results from different methods to obtain a more robust and reliable results of gene expression changes.
